                    <msContents>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="3r" to="31v"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6937NagaraMarAmh">Amharic version of Nagara Māryām</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="am">የእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ይትውልድዋ፡ የነገድዋ፡ ነገር፡ እንዴት፡ ነው፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="34v" to="44v"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6938MasNuzazeAmh">Amharic version of Maṣḥafa nuzāze</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="am">በስመ፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/> አሰርቅ፡ መዓልተ፡ ወሌሊተ። ተሣሃለነን፡ በል፡ እግዚኦ፡ መሐረነን፡ ፵፩፡ በእንተ፡ ማርያም፡ 
                                ፵፩በል፡ አቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ በል፡ እጽሕፍ፡ እንከ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ኑዛዜ፡ ዘይፈቅርዎ፡ መስተገብራን፡ ወይጻልዕዎ፡ ሀካያን፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
